<sup>a,</sup><sup>c</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Raikhelkar%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Jayant Raikhelkar</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Jayant Raikhelkar</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup>Seymour, Paul, and Gloria Milstein Division of Cardiology, Department of Medicine, Columbia University Irving Medical Center, New York, NY</div>
